      "body" : "Bohemian, you are right.  It appears the Eclipse IDE has problems evaluating expressions that contain strings containing escape sequences.  I didn&#39;t know that. I only use the Eclipse IDE to debug Java servlets. The eclipse expression evaluator will work for escaped stings if you add another level of escaping; which is why 4 backslashes worked for me but 2 wouldn&#39;t. Well that&#39;s life in the trenches!"
