      "body" : "@TomRutchik Expression evaluators will display <code>&quot;\\.&quot;</code> (the correct regex) for a String that is coded using the <i>String literal</i> <code>&quot;\\\\.&quot;</code> - to put a backslash (Hava&#39;s escape character) in a String when writing a String literal you escape the escape character."
