    "answer_id" : 14833055,
    "question_id" : 14833008,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I believe you should escape the dot. Try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String filename = \"D:/some folder/001.docx\";\nString extensionRemoved = filename.split(\"\\\\.\")[0];\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Otherwise dot is interpreted as any character in regular expressions.</p>\n"
  }, {
