    "body" : "<p>The dot &quot;.&quot; is a special character in java regex engine, so you have to use &quot;\\\\.&quot; to escape this character:</p>\n<pre><code>final String extensionRemoved = filename.split(&quot;\\\\.&quot;)[0];\n</code></pre>\n"
